{"tid":1136242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《復仇者聯盟4》帶動色情事業？外國名色情網站公布十大排名其中竟然超過一半係男人！！","createTime":"2019-05-03T01:09:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T02:00:37.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"61bdf50ff53ad5bdc81fb0e5324241520fe8f4d9","tid":1136242,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T01:09:03.000Z","msg":"由外國知名色情網站公布的數據，反映由4月初開始，跟復仇者聯盟有關的相關詞搜尋率得到大幅度的直線上升，甚至於4月19日左右，相關詞搜尋率已高達原本數據的3000％，對，是3000％！到底大家是想看誰喇&hellip;&hellip;？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n10大復仇者聯盟的情色榜排名<br />\n<br />\n貫徹不能劇透的傳統，就讓小編逐一為大家倒數復仇者聯盟的情色版本排名啦！<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/black-panther_1362654535cc73c3b87dc9-768x416.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2Fblack-panther_1362654535cc73c3b87dc9-768x416.jpg&h=526a497a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n10. 黑豹Black Panther<br />\n<br />\n黑豹Black Panther排第十<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n9. 鋼鐵人Iron Man<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/csydwa9b4jkp3xubegg1_14117161905cc73c39bb21f-768x432.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2Fcsydwa9b4jkp3xubegg1_14117161905cc73c39bb21f-768x432.jpeg&h=f95df3cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n人氣最強的 Iron Man 在「XXX幻想」世界似乎並非首選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n8. 雷神 Thor (只有第八位?!)<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/marvel_chris-hemsworth-shirtless_261017_1120_20010758415cc73c37f2b06-768x439.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2Fmarvel_chris-hemsworth-shirtless_261017_1120_20010758415cc73c37f2b06-768x439.jpg&h=6cd68ead&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n莫非受《復4》造型影響了男女性觀眾的幻想？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n7. 葛摩菈Gamora<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/gamora-untold-truth-guardians-780x438_rev1_11097529205cc73c36bc282-768x431.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2Fgamora-untold-truth-guardians-780x438_rev1_11097529205cc73c36bc282-768x431.jpg&h=1a7f8d5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n彩繪達人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4. 變形俠醫Hulk (這個排位是代表&hellip;&hellip;)<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/maxresdefault-3_1558468645cc7406b57ffd-768x432.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2Fmaxresdefault-3_1558468645cc7406b57ffd-768x432.jpg&h=96177a30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nHulk Smash!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 蜘蛛俠 Spider-Man<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/spiderman-5-1024x429.png.750x400_q85_box-1100914429_crop_detail_10062655685cc740692df43.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2Fspiderman-5-1024x429.png.750x400_q85_box-1100914429_crop_detail_10062655685cc740692df43.jpg&h=ed48e0a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n後生仔都唔放過<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nmplus.hk/690476/enterainment/%e5%be%a9%e4%bb%87%e8%80%85%e8%81%af%e7%9b%9f4-iron-man-%e9%bb%91%e5%af%a1%e5%a9%a6-scarlett-johansson/7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nmplus.hk%2F690476%2Fenterainment%2F%25e5%25be%25a9%25e4%25bb%2587%25e8%2580%2585%25e8%2581%25af%25e7%259b%259f4-iron-man-%25e9%25bb%2591%25e5%25af%25a1%25e5%25a9%25a6-scarlett-johansson%2F7%2F&d=YcIJTvf9PmU%2BR6jslv3gjAUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=668fcc46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nmplus.hk/690476/enterainment/%e5%be%a9%e4%bb%87%e8%80%85%e8%81%af%e7%9b%9f4-iron-man-%e9%bb%91%e5%af%a1%e5%a9%a6-scarlett-johansson/7/</a>"},{"pid":"80573b67a06ebf051a6c4b88148d3ec6d3c6663c","tid":1136242,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T01:10:54.000Z","msg":"第一名拋離幅度驚人<br />\n<br />\n雖然 Captain Marvel 的口碑好壞不一，亦有很多觀眾對於選角抱質疑心態，但看看下面